thread.title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Garden Bio-chemical High-tech sees Q1 2018 net profit up 610.9 pct to 640.1 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Garden Bio-chemical High-tech sees Q1 2018 net profit up 610.9 pct to 640.1 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - zhejiang garden bio-chemical high-tech co ltd

text:
Feb 5(Reuters) - Zhejiang Garden Bio-chemical High-tech Co Ltd
* Sees Q1 2018 net profit to increase by 610.9 percent to 640.1 percent, or to be 146 million yuan to 152 million yuan
* Says Q1 2017 net profit was 20.5 million yuan
* Says that sharply increased product sales price and increased product sales as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/KRvSQe
